{"word":"Ashes","slug":"ashes","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ashes</b> Uses of, in purification<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=10'>Num 19:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=17'>Num 19:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=13'>Heb 9:13</a><br/> A symbol of mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=19'>2Sa 13:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=4&verse=1'>Est 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=4&verse=3'>Est 4:3</a><br/> Sitting in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=2&verse=8'>Job 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=58&verse=5'>Isa 58:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=26'>Jer 6:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=30'>Eze 27:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=6'>Jon 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=13'>Luk 10:13</a><br/> Repenting in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=42&verse=6'>Job 42:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9&verse=3'>Dan 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=6'>Jon 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=21'>Mat 11:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=13'>Luk 10:13</a><br/> Disguises in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=38'>1Ki 20:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=41'>1Ki 20:41</a>"}]}